Yeah, it is pretty awesome.
Thanks for hanging out all day.

00:18:55.680 --> 00:18:58.810
Don't get mushy,
the pleasure's all mine.

00:18:58.890 --> 00:19:01.180
I can't believe you
even brought a cake.

00:19:01.270 --> 00:19:03.060
But I do feel kinda bad
that you went through

00:19:03.140 --> 00:19:04.810
so much trouble for me.

00:19:04.890 --> 00:19:05.980
Not to ruin the mood,

00:19:06.060 --> 00:19:08.020
but I'm not sure how
to return the favor.

00:19:08.110 --> 00:19:10.240
Listen, there's no need to
worry your messy little head

00:19:10.320 --> 00:19:12.740
about any of that when
you're the man of the hour.

