That's real sweet of you,
but still.

00:19:14.860 --> 00:19:17.070
[UZAKI]
Uh. Ooh, I know. How about this?

00:19:17.160 --> 00:19:20.080
If you want, you could always
try to hit me back next year.

00:19:20.160 --> 00:19:22.450
You're not the only one
with a birthday, ya know?

00:19:22.540 --> 00:19:24.670
[SAKURAI] Mm. Guess we could
celebrate yours, too.

00:19:24.750 --> 00:19:26.840
