leaving the house.

00:19:34.380 --> 00:19:36.010
Points towards what now?

00:19:36.090 --> 00:19:37.930
Points towards your Uzakimiles!

00:19:38.010 --> 00:19:41.140
[SAKURAI] Uzakimiles?
