00:19:41.220 --> 00:19:43.930
[SAKURAI] Maybe it's 'cause
I've been hitting the gym,

00:19:44.020 --> 00:19:46.980
but I feel like my head's
gotten a lot clearer.

00:19:47.060 --> 00:19:49.440
