Whenever she's making a fuss,

00:19:54.030 --> 00:19:56.410
I know it's only
because she cares.

00:19:56.490 --> 00:19:58.530
No matter what kind
of messes we get into,

00:19:58.620 --> 00:20:03.290
it really is fun hanging out.
She makes it fun.

