Damn, she got me good. I
actually wanna return the favor.

00:20:07.620 --> 00:20:10.540
Better not let on, though.
It'll go straight to her head.

00:20:10.630 --> 00:20:12.760
I'll try to keep that
in mind for next year.

00:20:12.840 --> 00:20:14.130
Whaddaya mean, you'll try?

00:20:14.210 --> 00:20:16.210
I wanna hear you say
that you'll do it.

00:20:16.300 --> 00:20:18.090
All right, whatever,
it's a promise.

00:20:18.180 --> 00:20:19.890
If we commit to this,
we could make it

00:20:19.970 --> 00:20:21.470
a regular thing from now on!

00:20:21.550 --> 00:20:22.930
Let's not get carried away.

00:20:23.010 --> 00:20:24.640
[UZAKI laughing]

00:20:24.720 --> 00:20:27.310
[SAKURAI] I mean, after next
year, I'll be graduating.

00:20:27.390 --> 00:20:28.850
Huh?

00:20:31.610 --> 00:20:35.320
[SAKURAI]
Hm? Uzaki?

00:20:35.400 --> 00:20:36.690
[UZAKI gasping]

00:20:36.780 --> 00:20:38.950
[UZAKI]
It's just like what Sakaki said.

00:20:39.030 --> 00:20:41.280
[SAKAKI] You might want to make
a move sooner rather than later.

00:20:41.370 --> 00:20:42.910
[UZAKI]
That jerk was right.

00:20:42.990 --> 00:20:45.580
I've only got a year
and some change left.

00:20:45.660 --> 00:20:49.750
What am I supposed to do
with so little time?

00:20:49.830 --> 00:20:52.830
And this idiot doesn't even
seem to be in any kind of hurry.

00:20:52.920 --> 00:20:54.300
What a pain.

00:20:54.380 --> 00:20:55.800
Ugh. At this rate,

00:20:55.880 --> 00:20:59.970
he's totally gonna graduate
without knowing how I feel.

00:21:00.050 --> 00:21:02.140
And after that...

00:21:02.220 --> 00:21:04.100
I...

00:21:04.180 --> 00:21:06.640
I'll never get to...

00:21:08.690 --> 00:21:10.820
[UZAKI]
Uh. Hey, Sakurai?

00:21:10.900 --> 00:21:11.860
[SAKURAI]
What's up?

00:21:11.940 --> 00:21:15.150
[UZAKI]
I, uh... Well you see, I...

00:21:15.230 --> 00:21:17.480
I was just thinking that...

00:21:17.570 --> 00:21:19.990
Seems you got something
serious on your mind.

00:21:20.070 --> 00:21:21.240
[UZAKI]
Mm-hm...

00:21:21.320 --> 00:21:23.410
[SAKURAI] Well, it's
real honesty hours now.

00:21:23.490 --> 00:21:25.160
You can let it out.

00:21:27.120 --> 00:21:28.370
No more hiding.

00:21:28.460 --> 00:21:31.300
I hope that you're ready
for things to get sincere.

00:21:31.370 --> 00:21:32.580
[SAKURAI]
Go ahead.

00:21:32.670 --> 00:21:35.050
I was thinking...

00:21:35.130 --> 00:21:36.380
[gasps]

00:21:38.010 --> 00:21:42.100
How 'bout getting
held back a year?

00:21:42.180 --> 00:21:44.310
[SAKURAI] What? Why the hell
would I risk my degree?!

00:21:44.390 --> 00:21:45.980
So you can have more
time to hang out with

00:21:46.060 --> 00:21:48.310
your favorite person
before you walk, obviously!

00:21:48.390 --> 00:21:50.310
[SAKURAI] Do you have any
idea how crazy you sound?

00:21:50.390 --> 00:21:52.810
[UZAKI] You'll be eligible to
earn triple the Uzakimiles

00:21:52.900 --> 00:21:54.400
if you let yourself
